	<div class="explainer-card__content">
		

<figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img src="https://calmatters.org/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2020/02/AP_TrumpFresno_022520_01.jpg?w=1024" alt="Republican presidential candidate Donald Trump gestures during a rally, Friday, May 27, 2016, in Fresno, Calif. Photo by Chris Carlson, AP Photo" class="wp-image-102811" srcset="https://calmatters.org/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2020/02/AP_TrumpFresno_022520_01.jpg?w=2000 2000w, https://calmatters.org/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2020/02/AP_TrumpFresno_022520_01.jpg?w=300 300w, https://calmatters.org/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2020/02/AP_TrumpFresno_022520_01.jpg?w=768 768w, https://calmatters.org/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2020/02/AP_TrumpFresno_022520_01.jpg?w=1024 1024w, https://calmatters.org/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2020/02/AP_TrumpFresno_022520_01.jpg?w=1536 1536w, https://calmatters.org/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2020/02/AP_TrumpFresno_022520_01.jpg?w=439 439w, https://calmatters.org/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2020/02/AP_TrumpFresno_022520_01.jpg?w=307 307w, https://calmatters.org/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2020/02/AP_TrumpFresno_022520_01.jpg?w=780 780w, https://calmatters.org/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2020/02/AP_TrumpFresno_022520_01.jpg?w=820 820w, https://calmatters.org/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2020/02/AP_TrumpFresno_022520_01.jpg?w=758 758w" sizes="(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px" /><figcaption>Republican presidential candidate Donald Trump gestures during a rally, Friday, May 27, 2016, in Fresno, Calif. Photo by Chris Carlson, AP Photo</figcaption></figure>



<p>In 2019, the Trump administration introduced a <a href="https://calmatters.org/environment/2019/10/trump-plan-could-bring-growers-more-water-but-will-it-harm-californias-rare-salmon/">plan</a> that critics say weakens Endangered Species Act restrictions on pumping water from the Delta.</p>



<p>Many farmers welcome the proposal since it could increase their annual water deliveries by half a million acre-feet or more. But environmentalists call it “an extinction plan” for winter-run Chinook salmon and Delta smelt. They say it will allow more diversions during key migration periods, increasing the odds the fish will be sucked into the pumps, and it may affect spawning salmon. Newsom has threatened to sue the federal government to halt the plan.</p>

	</div>

	<div class="explainer-card-footer">
		<span class="explainer-card__footer-copyright">&copy; 2020</span>
